<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>SJB — Election Results</title>

  <!-- Bootstrap 5 & Icons -->
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"/>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.3/font/bootstrap-icons.min.css" rel="stylesheet"/>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@600;700;800;900&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>

  <style>
    :root{
      --navy:#1B2A4A;
      --gold:#C9972B;
      --gold-lt:#E8B84B;
      --cream:#F8F5EF;
      --slate:#6B7A99;
      --white:#fff;
      --card-shadow:0 8px 32px rgba(27, 42, 74, .13);
    }
    *{ box-sizing:border-box; }
    body{
      font-family:'Inter', sans-serif;
      background:var(--cream);
      color:var(--navy);
      min-height:100vh;
    }
    .site-header{
      background:var(--navy);
      padding:18px 0 14px;
      border-bottom:4px solid var(--gold);
      position:sticky; top:0; z-index:100;
    }
    .school-crest{
      width:54px; height:54px;
      background:var(--gold);
      border-radius:50%;
      display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
      font-size:1.6rem; font-weight:800; color:var(--navy);
      font-family:'Playfair Display', serif;
      flex-shrink:0;
    }
    .hero{
      background:linear-gradient(135deg, var(--navy) 60%, #2e4578 100%);
      color:var(--white);
      padding:56px 0 44px;
      text-align:center;
      position:relative;
      overflow:hidden;
    }
    .hero::before{
      content:'';
      position:absolute;
      top:-50%; right:-20%;
      width:400px; height:400px;
      background:rgba(201,151,43,.08);
      border-radius:50%;
    }
    .hero::after{
      content:'';
      position:absolute;
      bottom:-30%; left:-10%;
      width:300px; height:300px;
      background:rgba(201,151,43,.06);
      border-radius:50%;
    }
    .badge-election{
      background:var(--gold) !important;
      color:var(--navy) !important;
      font-weight:900;
      padding:8px 20px !important;
      border-radius:999px;
      display:inline-flex;
      gap:10px;
      align-items:center;
      position:relative;
      z-index:1;
    }
    .hero-title{
      font-family:'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-weight:900;
      font-size:2.5rem;
      position:relative; z-index:1;
      margin-top:10px;
    }
    .hero-sub{
      color:rgba(255,255,255,.78);
      position:relative; z-index:1;
      max-width:780px;
      margin:10px auto 0;
      font-size:1.05rem;
    }

    .main{
      padding:22px 0 64px;
    }
    .card-landing{
      background:var(--white);
      border-radius:18px;
      box-shadow:var(--card-shadow);
      padding:34px 26px;
      max-width:780px;
      margin:-26px auto 0;
      border:1px solid rgba(27,42,74,.06);
    }

    .winner-chip{
      display:inline-flex;
      gap:10px;
      align-items:center;
      padding:10px 16px;
      border-radius:999px;
      background:linear-gradient(135deg, var(--gold) 0%, var(--gold-lt) 100%);
      color:var(--navy);
      font-weight:900;
      box-shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(201,151,43,.18);
    }

    .btn-gold{
      background:linear-gradient(135deg, var(--gold) 0%, var(--gold-lt) 100%);
      color:var(--navy);
      border:none;
      border-radius:14px;
      padding:14px 18px;
      font-weight:900;
      box-shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(201,151,43,.18);
      text-decoration:none;
      display:inline-flex;
      align-items:center;
      justify-content:center;
      gap:10px;
      width:100%;
    }
    .btn-outline-navy{
      background:transparent;
      color:var(--navy);
      border:2px solid rgba(27,42,74,.18);
      border-radius:14px;
      padding:14px 18px;
      font-weight:900;
      text-decoration:none;
      display:inline-flex;
      align-items:center;
      justify-content:center;
      gap:10px;
      width:100%;
    }

    .btn-row{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap:12px;
      margin-top:22px;
    }
    @media (max-width: 560px){
      .btn-row{ grid-template-columns:1fr; }
      .hero-title{ font-size:2.1rem; }
    }

    .note{
      margin-top:18px;
      color:var(--slate);
      font-size:.95rem;
      line-height:1.6;
      text-align:center;
    }

    footer a{ color:var(--slate); text-decoration:none; }
    footer a:hover{ color:var(--navy); text-decoration:underline; }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <header class="site-header">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-3">
        <div class="school-crest">SJB</div>
        <div>
          <h1 class="text-white mb-0" style="font-size:1.25rem;">St. Josephine Bakhita</h1>
          <small style="color:#E8B84B;">United OBs &amp; OGs — Official Election</small>
        </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="badge-election mb-2">
        <i class="bi bi-patch-check-fill"></i> 2025 / 2026 Elections
      </div>
      <div class="hero-title">Voting Closed</div>
      <div class="hero-sub">
        No one is supposed to vote now. Proceed to the announced results and the printable thank-you document.
      </div>
  </section>

  <main class="main">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="card-landing text-center">
        <div class="winner-chip">
          <i class="bi bi-trophy-fill"></i>
          Winner: <span style="color:var(--gold);">Nakaliisa Hadijah</span>
        </div>

        <div class="btn-row">
          <a class="btn-gold" href="results.html">
            <i class="bi bi-bar-chart-fill"></i>
            View Results
          </a>
          <a class="btn-outline-navy" href="thank_you_participants.html" target="_blank">
            <i class="bi bi-file-earmark-pdf"></i>
            Thank You (PDF)
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="note">
          Chairperson: <strong>Nakaliisa Hadijah</strong> <span style="color:rgba(27,42,74,.45);">•</span>
          Total votes cast: <strong>18</strong>
        </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer class="text-center py-4 text-muted small">
    United OBs &amp; OGs of St. Josephine Bakhita<br>
    Contact: <a href="mailto:ssemwogerere.ashiraf@stud.umu.ac.ug">ssemwogerere.ashiraf@stud.umu.ac.ug</a> |
    <a href="https://wa.me/256701422100" target="_blank">WhatsApp +256 701 422 100</a>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
